WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.539
Hola nens.

00:00:02.539 --> 00:00:04.099
(Rialles)

00:00:04.099 --> 00:00:06.683
Tinc 71 anys.

00:00:06.683 --> 00:00:08.778
(Aplaudiments)

00:00:08.778 --> 00:00:11.580
El meu marit en té 76.

00:00:11.580 --> 00:00:15.040
Els meus pares 90 i molts,

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:17.730
i l'Olivia, la gossa, en té 16.

00:00:17.740 --> 00:00:20.130
Parlem d'envellir.

00:00:20.130 --> 00:00:21.678
Deixeu-me dir-vos com em sento

00:00:21.678 --> 00:00:23.875
quan veig les meves arrugues al mirall

00:00:23.875 --> 00:00:27.200
i me n'adono que algunes parts
han començat a caure

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:29.832
i que ja no les trobo allà baix.

00:00:29.832 --> 00:00:30.970
(Rialles)